Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_VipPortEmbConfig::errCorrEnable

TRUE: Error Correction enable, FALSE: disabled.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortEmbConfig::reserved

Previously isMaxChan3Bits - missing from header file FALSE: Use all 5 bits of the field for 32 total sources, TRUE : Use only bits 2:0 of this field to support the TVP5158's 8 sources, with the two upper most bits reserved.
